QuestData.Title: Charged Moganite
QuestData.Description: We have been dispatching spies into the Sunreaver base of operations on a daily basis. Some had orders to recover charged moganite from the enemy and bring it here.$b$bThey have not returned, and I can confirm they have left the Sunreaver base.$b$bSearch the jungle between here and there and find any of the charged moganite that might have been lost in transit. Bring it to me and we will put it to good use.
QuestData.LogDescription: Recover a Charged Moganite and bring it to Warmage Yurias.

Objectives.Objective: Charged Moganite returned to Violet Rise
